  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction à GNOME Screensaver</title>
    <para>
      The <application>GNOME Screensaver</application> package contains a
      screen saver et locker designed to have simple, sane, secure defaults
      et be well integrated with the desktop. It supports locking down of
      configuration settings, has translations into many languages et
      convenient user switching.
    </para>
    &lfs72_checked;
